 CBNuGridKey args;id;eventName;src;logMsg;currentLog;gridId;editId
‚ćĚ KeyPress duplicate-repro callback for DemoNuGridKeyPress (review finding #14).
‚ćĚ The server delivers events flattened as (ID Event),Info ‚ÄĒ EWC/processEvent.aplf:91 ‚ÄĒ
‚ćĚ so ‚äÉargs is the SOURCE object ID and 2‚äÉargs is the event name (same shape
‚ćĚ CBNuGrid.aplf:6-7 relies on). We log a DISTINCT, unambiguous label per source
‚ćĚ (GRID vs EDIT) plus the raw id, so a human/test can count how many KeyPress
‚ćĚ events fire for one keystroke and see which object emitted each.
‚ćĚ Source-branching idiom: CBGrid2.aplf (:Select ‚äÉmsg), CBUpdateScroll.aplf:51.

 id‚Üź‚äÉargs
 eventName‚Üź2‚äÉargs
 gridId‚Üź'F1.G'
 editId‚Üź'F1.G.E1'

 :Select eventName
 :Case 'KeyPress'
     ‚ćĚ Info: [key, charCode, keyCode, shiftState] (Info[1] is at 3‚äÉargs)
     :Select id
     :Case gridId
         src‚Üź'GRID'
     :Case editId
         src‚Üź'EDIT'
     :Else
         src‚Üź'OTHER'
     :EndSelect
     logMsg‚Üźsrc,' KeyPress key="',(‚ćē3‚äÉargs),'" shift=',(‚ćē6‚äÉargs),' (id=',id,')'
 :Case 'CellMove'
     ‚ćĚ Info: [row, col, scrollFlag, selectionFlag, mouseFlag, ...]
     logMsg‚Üź'----- CellMove Row ',(‚ćē3‚äÉargs),' Col ',(‚ćē4‚äÉargs),' -----'
 :Else
     logMsg‚Üźid,' ',eventName,': ',‚ćē2‚Üďargs
 :EndSelect

‚ćĚ Prepend the new line to the Log label (CBNuGrid.aplf:54-55 idiom).
 currentLog‚Üź'F1.Log'eWG'Caption'
 'F1.Log'eWS'Caption'(logMsg,(‚éēUCS 10),currentLog)
